],"#Workflow Automation#Anti-Patterns#❌ No Observability":[51,52],"#Workflow Automation#⚠️ Sharp Edges":[53,65],"#Workflow Automation#⚠️ Sharp Edges#{1}":[55,65],"#Workflow Automation#Related Skills":[66,69],"#Workflow Automation#Related Skills#{1}":[68,69]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"name":"workflow-automation","description":"Workflow automation is the infrastructure that makes AI agents reliable. Without durable execution, a network hiccup during a 10-step payment flow means lost money and angry customers. With it, workflows resume exactly where they left off.  This skill covers the platforms (n8n, Temporal, Inngest) and patterns (sequential, parallel, orchestrator-worker) that turn brittle scripts into production-grade automation.  Key insight: The platforms make different tradeoffs. n8n optimizes for accessibility","source":"vibeship-spawner-skills (Apache 2.0)"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"00_System/Links/App_agent_skills_repo/workflow-automation/SKILL.md"},
